25/03/2005
WASHINGTON, United States -- Secretary of State Condoleezza Rice met with Greek Foreign Minister Petros Molyviatis on Thursday (24 March). 
They focused on the latest events in Kyrgyzstan, and especially on the OSCE's lead role in international efforts to direct events there towards a peaceful, democratic outcome. 
The two officials also expressed satisfaction with the state of relations between their countries. 
(MPA, VoA - 24/03/05)
